stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> KickerOff : wanted = IDLE
    [*] --> KickerReversing : wanted = REVERSING

    [*] --> KickerSpinningUp : wanted = KICKING

    KickerSpinningUp --> KickerAtSetpoint : velocity within tolerance [debounced]
    KickerAtSetpoint --> KickerRecovering : ball fired [velocity dip past debounce]
    KickerRecovering --> KickerAtSetpoint : velocity recovered to tolerance
    KickerRecovering --> UnderKicking : sustained RPM drop [0.2s debounce]
    UnderKicking --> KickerSpinningUp : wanted state re-entered

    note right of KickerSpinningUp
        Aggressive spinup control.
        Max acceleration.
    end note

    note right of KickerAtSetpoint
        Hold velocity control.
        Target: 3500 RPM.
    end note

    note right of KickerRecovering
        Re-spinning after note pass.
        Kick count incremented.
    end note

    note right of UnderKicking
        Too many rapid notes.
        Kicker cannot recover.
    end note
